<refsect1 id="GstGLUpload.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para><link linkend="GstGLUpload"><type>GstGLUpload</type></link> is an object that uploads data from system memory into GL textures.</para>
<para>A <link linkend="GstGLUpload"><type>GstGLUpload</type></link> can be created with <link linkend="gst-gl-upload-new"><function>gst_gl_upload_new()</function></link></para>

</refsect1>
